name: Digital Lab - Corporate template
description:
Corporate website with a unique design and a huge number of pages. The design is made in a unique and innovative design that will allow you to create a beautiful and selling page design.


You can change the design theme without a problem, we did everything in layers and made it as convenient as possible so that you can quickly and easily change the design of your future site.


Functions


- 20+ full layer Adobe Photoshop .PSD and Figma files

- Designed with responsiveness in mind

- Clean, modern design

- Well organized layers make it very easy to update

- All fonts used in templates are available in Google Font.
